## Set issue Status to "In progress" (after creating the branch)

Required whether the branch was created via MCP **`create_branch`** or locally (fallback). Set the issue's **project Status to "In progress"** (ReAIty Check project only). Use the **Projects toolset** to update the project item's Status. If the tool is unavailable, add an issue comment asking the user to move the card to In progress.

